data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome home to this charming two bedroom two bath home in a quiet subdivision.  Spacious open floor plan with tile floors throughout.  Large master bedroom with ensuite bath.  Large two car garage with washer and dryer hookups.  Newer roofing AC unit.  This home is close to amenities and is just a few minutes drive from Anclote Beach and historic Tarpon Springs.
